Sentencas: Bilayered electrolyte membranes composed of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3 - delta, (BZCY) and Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 - delta (SDC) were evaluated for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), and the influence of the membrane architecture on the cell performance was investigated.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: The electrochemical testing results showed that the electron-blocking ability of BZCY layer depends on its exact location in the fuel cell.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: The partial internal short circuit was nearly totally eliminated for the cell with BZCY layer located at the anode side, and the corresponding cell exhibited a high open circuit voltage (OCV) of 1.0 V at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: In contrast, the cell with BZCY layer located at the cathode side still exhibited significant internal short-circuit behavior.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: The different electron-blocking ability can be ascribed to the atmosphere-dependent charge transport behavior of BZCY.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: The present results demonstrate that the bilayered BZCY/SDC membrane with BZCY layer located at the anode side is a promising electrolyte for highly efficient low-temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages

Sentencas: Besides, the BZCY layer should be as thin as possible to achieve desirable power performance for the fuel cell.
Titulo: Bilayered BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ electrolyte membranes for solid oxide fuel cells with high open circuit voltages
